Typically, the test class keeps strong reference to the mock object and it prevents getting the mock collected. Mockito internally needs to keep weak references to mock objects to avoid memory leaks for certain types of MockMaker implementations. If you see this exception using Mockito public API, please file a bug. For more information see issue #1313.
